social_posts.post_text: Giving boogie Bamm-Bamm ✨

Took this months ago but still gonna use it as my birthday post anyway because I feel hot in it✌️
Here’s to my late 20s 🥳🎂
A birthday trip to Dublin followed by a night out back home to some of America’s favorite haunts — @daveandbusters @applebees @eaglenyc 🍀👾🍎🦅

Hi friends! After a one year hiatus, I’m making my Broadway Bares return! And I honestly could not be more excited to be back. But here’s where you come in! I need help raising money for the incredible organization Broadway Cares/Equity Fights AIDS. Please follow the link in my bio and donate as much as you can to help people in need! Thank you so much ☺️ #BroadwayBares
This girl is ready for summer…and is also jealous of everyone’s fire island pics this weekend so is posting one from last summer 🙈🤷‍♀️

Looking at your donation to my #BroadwayBares fundraiser on the first day of rehearsal like…😏😜
Extremely pumped to be back in the room dancing for @bcefa today! Please follow the link in my bio and let’s make a difference together!!
📸: @norbertgarciajr

Pointe me to the donations for #BroadwayBares 🩰😜
Yes I know I’m not on pointe but @olivecotham suggested this caption and it made me giggle. Just a little over a week to donate to my fundraiser for @bcefa! There’s no time like now to help me raise money by following the link in my bio!! 🤗

📸: @patricklupinski

Hi girlies!! Only one week left to donate to my #BroadwayBares fundraising page! Help me reach (and hopefully raise 😋) my goal for @bcefa! 
Link in bio 🤗🤗
📸: @norbertgarciajr

It’s the week of the show, y’all! Who’s coming to see #BroadwayBares this upcoming Sunday?! I hope to see many familiar faces there. And whether you can or can’t come to the show, I’d love your support in my fundraising efforts for @bcefa! Follow the link in my bio to donate 😘
📸: @patricklupinski

WE BROKE MY FIRST GOAL FOR BROADWAY BARES!! 🎊 Thank you to everyone who has donated so far. I am so grateful to all of you! 🤗
We still have 2 more days to raise money for the event, so I’ve raised my goal! If you haven’t had the chance to donate yet to @bcefa, follow the link in my bio and help me break another goal!! 😘
📸: @norbertgarciajr

‼️FINAL CALL FOR DONATIONS‼️
If you haven’t donated to my #BroadwayBares page yet, now is the time! Please help me in my final push to raise money for the incredible organization @bcefa!! Link in bio!! 🤗

Returning to #BroadwayBares was such a magical experience!! Truly couldn’t have asked for a better cast to do this number with. And thanks to all of you, we raised $10k for @bcefa through my personal fundraising efforts! AND the event itself raised a grand total of $1,887,014!!! Thank you all for making this Bares such a wonderful one! 🥹🤗
Figured I should probably post the fire island pictures from earlier this month before I go back out in 2 days 😅🙈
